{
  "id": "adv_bond_mhk_01_02",
  "title": "miho2",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_02-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "それでね、大学のレポートを提出したと思ったんだけど\nよく見たら、こっそり作ってた曲の歌詞だったのよぉ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ I thought I'd turned in my college report‚\nbut looking closely‚ those were the lyrics to a song I had secretly composed",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 14.5066663425
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_02-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "教授には凄い嫌味言われるし\n歌詞は、怜ちゃんにダメ出しされるしぃ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I got scolded a lot by professor\nAs for the lyrics‚ I heard Rei-chan said no…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.5066663425,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 23.0966666222
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_02-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "……はぁ。なんで私、こんな酔っ払いの愚痴を\n延々と聞かされてるのかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Haa. Why do I have to keep listening to\nthis drunk's complain",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.0966666222,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 30.1128340404
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_02-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "むむっ？　mihoさん、あんまり飲んでないわね～？\n飲め～、飲みなさいよぉ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mmm? miho-san‚ you don't drink much~?\nDrink~‚ drink~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.1128340404,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 40.9727432569
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_02-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "……一人にしておいてくれたら飲むわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I'll drink if you leave me alone",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.9727432569,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 43.6549201172
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_02-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "……まったく。貴方、まだ二十歳でしょう？\nもうこんなに飲んだくれになって、将来どうするのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "….Seriously. You're only 20‚ aren't you?\nYou've become such a alcoholic already‚ what are you going to do with your future",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.6549201172,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 51.9992515406
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_02-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "遙子、飲んだくれじゃないもん～\nちょ～っと、お酒が好きなだけだもん～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko‚ not a alcoholic~\njust like drink a little bit~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.9992515406,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 60.3696144264
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_02-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "最初にお酒飲んだ時は、変な味って思ったけど\n何回か飲んでるうちに美味しくなってきてぇ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The first drank it‚ I thought it tasted weird‚\nbut after a few drinks‚ it started to taste good",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.3696144264,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_02-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ、ねぇねぇ\nmihoさんが最初にお酒飲んだ時はどうだったの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right‚ hey-hey\nWhat was it like the first time you tried drink‚ miho-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.1493196965,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 80.8241496246
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_02-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "私の話はいいでしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Enough of my story",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.8241496246,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 82.932426246
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_02-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "え～、教えてよぉ～\n遙子～、mihoさんのこともっともーっと知りたーい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh~‚ tell me~\nHaruko~‚ wants to know moreー about miho-sanー",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.932426246,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 93.4179134846
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_02-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……これは長くなりそうだわ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa… it's going to be long…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.4179134846,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 98.8455323379
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_02-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "すぅー、すぅー……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sniffー‚ sniffー…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.8788651626,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 108.4379581769
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_02-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅ、ようやく落ち着いたわね\nでも、最初にお酒を飲んだ時……か……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Phew‚ it's finally calming down\nBut‚ when I first drank… drink…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.4379581769,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 118.2673009872
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_02-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "二十歳の誕生日だったのよね\n葉ちゃんと一緒に……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was my 20th birthday\nWith You-chan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.2673009872,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_02-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "誕生日は葉ちゃんの方が早かったけど\n私が飲めるようになるまで待っててくれたっけ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You-chan's birthday was earlier\nBut she waited until I was old enough to drink",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.8503822167,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 129.2404272238
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_02-mhk009.m4a",
      "text": "……ああ、でも、一口、口を付けただけだったな\nそれで、甘くて美味しいとか、いや苦い、だなんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yeah‚ but‚ I only took one sip\nSo‚ I said it was sweet and delicious‚ no it seemed bitter",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.2404272238,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_02-mhk010.m4a",
      "text": "ああだこうだと話してるうちに閉店になって\n……懐かしいわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "While we were talking‚ the bar closed\n…I miss it",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.091606156,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 144.3090891361
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_02-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "……ん、み、mihoしゃ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Umm‚ m-miho-sa…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.3090891361,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 150.8403877418
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_02-mhk011.m4a",
      "text": "っ、驚いた……起きたのかと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ surprised… did she wake up…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.8403877418,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 155.0107278984
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_02-mhk012.m4a",
      "text": "私としたことが、寝てるとはいえ遙子がいるところで\n迂闊だったわね。……割と酔ってるのかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What am I doing in front of Haruko‚ even though she's asleep\nI was fool. …Am I drunker than I thought",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.0107278984,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 163.5429045519
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_02-mhk013.m4a",
      "text": "さっさと遙子をタクシーに押し込んで帰りましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let's quickly push Haruko into the taxi and go home",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.5429045519,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}